{
  "stem": "11844.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, I'd like our soccer team to become part of the Dutch Soccer Association.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I translated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's the Nederland [SPEAKING DUTCH], the Dutch Soccer [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Moise Katznelson, who had a very Eastern European-- Eastern Jewish European mentality, said, no way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It will create problems.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if our soccer team goes into the little villages around-- by they way, Nieuwesluis-- Werkdorp Nieuwesluis-- was all the way in the north of Holland, next to a small city by the name of Schagen, about two hours by train away from Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Katznelson, no way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It will create problems.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It will create problems with the population of the area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I say, you don't know what you're talking about because nothing unites people more than sport, and art, and science.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It will make us popular.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "People will like us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It will be wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I did a few-- did a little bit politicking and the soccer team of the Jewish Werkdorp Nieuwesluis became part of the Dutch Soccer Association.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That took place in middle '39.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Let's say July, August, September, that area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we-- every Sunday, you know, we went to various communities in the area for the game.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was C class, not A or B class.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was my victory, by the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's nothing to do with what we are talking about, really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but it was an organization that you were involved in, in a very trying time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was right, by the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It endeared-- no-- no, not endeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It brought us close to many of the rural population in that area, and that helped a great deal the years after in the underground situation.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
